&lt;p&gt;St Austell area Community nurses are looking for a dynamic team leader to cover the innovative PCN area of St Austell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;St Austell has a large team of nurses covering a diverse community and works closely with the innovative practice of St Austell Healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The St Austell area is known for working in new and innovative ways and this is a fantastic opportunity to join the team as a dynamic and passionate leader with a vision for change and the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team consists of 14 nurses and 4 HCAs covering the geographical area of Penwithick to Gorran to Carlyon Bay and is predominantly based inh St Austell Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fast pace team and offers excitement and variety in comparison to a traditional community nursing team with the opportunity to develop services around the needs of the immediate community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact us- 01726 873090&lt;/p&gt;
